      "content": "It's incredibly hard when those we rely on for support don't seem to understand the depth of what we're going through. Rebuilding after such a profound loss is a very personal journey and takes time. Have you considered individual therapy or support groups where you can connect with others who might be experiencing similar feelings? Sometimes sharing with those who have been through similar situations can provide unique and understanding perspectives, and help in healing the void you're experiencing.",
      "source": "target",
